tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE PerformanceLogs (
  log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  action VARCHAR,
  duration INT
)

CREATE TABLE log_data (
    timestamp TIMESTAMP PRIMARY KEY,
    query_id INT,
    query_text TEXT,
    execution_time FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE performance_metrics (
    metric_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    dbms_name TEXT,
    cpu_utilization FLOAT,
    memory_utilization FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE optimization_data (
    optimization_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    query_id INT,
    optimization_steps TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE database_info (
    db_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    db_name TEXT,
    db_version TEXT,
    created_on DATE
)

CREATE TABLE log_data (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    log_time TIMESTAMP,
    user_id INT,
    query TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE performance_metrics (
    metric_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    metric_name VARCHAR(50),
    metric_value FLOAT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE optimization_settings (
    setting_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    setting_name VARCHAR(50),
    setting_value FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE user_activity (
    activity_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    activity_type VARCHAR(50),
    activity_time TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE error_logs (
    error_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    log_id INT,
    error_message TEXT,
    error_time TIMESTAMP
)
